data.description: Take the long meandering drive to your private, wooded oasis on 12+acres!  This cottage-style home boasts cozy wood paneling throughout and an open concept living plan! Natural light floods the home including the well appointed kitchen featuring granite counters, stainless appliances, subway tile backsplash and kitchen island.  Laundry is a breeze in the cute dedicated laundry area hidden behind a beautiful, custom barn door! The Primary suite is spacious and serviced by its own private en suite bathroom. The additional bedroom is very cute. There's a secondary bathroom for guests as well.  You'll enjoy endless hours of relaxation on the back deck overlooking your property which is ripe with possibilities from hiking, trail riding to gardening or even a hobby farm!   Some of the property is fenced already for animals and additional outbuildings including a 12x20 utility shed are ready for your smaller farm animals or storage. The detached two car garage/shop is 30x30 and the perfect place to house all of your toys too! Come make this your little piece of paradise!
